snippet.title: NES Game: Vs. Stroke & Match [Ladies Version] (1984 Nintendo)
snippet.description:
A sports/golf game. 

An arcade golf game running on Nintendo's Vs arcade system. 

Note: Since this was played on an NES emulator, I'm marking it as an NES game.
